 Sir, London has greater claim to be the world centre for sustainable development than Spain's Soria ("Medieval city takes the long view on jobs", February 12). A world centre must be an exemplar not only in its local economic development and its built \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2  but also in the support that it provides to the sustainable development of the world.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 London's unsung cluster of sustainability and \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  expertise may put us ahead of any other city in our impact on world sustainability. Champions such as SustainAbility, AccountAbility and Forum for the Future started in London and are still based here. Our finance sector hosts world-leading expertise in socially responsible investment. The London-based sustainability practices in the leading consultancies probably regard only their Amsterdam colleagues as significant competitors. London's architecture and engineering skills support sustainable development worldwide.\par \par \uc2 Our diversity gives us influence worldwide via family relationships as well as business and contributes significantly to our expertise in social sustainability. And, at last, it seems that our physical infrastructure and resource management may begin to catch up.\par \par \uc2 You rightly highlight the significant opportunity offered by the title of "world centre for sustainable development". London should boldly stake its claim.\par \par \uc2 Penny Shepherd, Chief Executive, London Sustainability Exchange, London EC1V 3QN \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b NS\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 ccsr : \uc2 Corporate Social Responsibility | c152 : \uc2 Earnings Projections | gdip : \uc2 International Relations | genv : \uc2 Environmental News | nanl : \uc2 Analysis | c15 : \uc2 Performance | ccat : \uc2 Corporate/Industrial News | gcat : \uc2 Political/General News | ncat : \uc2 Content Types\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b RE\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 uk : \uc2 United Kingdom | eecz : \uc2 European Union Countries | eurz : \uc2 Europe | weurz : \uc2 Western Europe\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b PUB\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 The Financial Times Limited (AAIW/EIW)\ce